retz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-unanimously-rejects-unilateral-intl-recognition-of-palestinian-state/0000018d-bcbe-dd5e-a59d-fdbe1d020000</guid></item><item><title>在美国的限制下，受制裁的以色列定居者共同拥有的公司在其兄弟名下注册</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/company-of-sanctioned-israeli-settler-registered-under-his-brother-amid-restrictions/0000018d-bc42-dc8c-a3df-fe7719280000</link><description>美国对约旦河西岸活动家伊农·莱维实施制裁后，他表示公司银行账户已被冻结，而他的兄弟则否认制裁后登记了所有权变更</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 14:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/company-of-sanctioned-israeli-settler-registered-under-his-brother-amid-restrictions/0000018d-bc42-dc8c-a3df-fe7719280000</guid></item><item><title>在花费数年时间使以色列两极分化之后，内塔尼亚胡将团结作为武器来对抗异见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/after-spending-years-polarizing-israel-netanyahu-uses-unity-as-a-weapon-against-dissent/0000018d-bc12-df10-a99f-bff397fe0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡曾经证明，对他来说，战争为另一场政治运动提供了一个平台，其特点是所有熟悉的特征：谎言、煽动、煽动激情和转移注意力</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 13:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/after-spending-years-polarizing-israel-netanyahu-uses-unity-as-a-weapon-against-dissent/0000018d-bc12-df10-a99f-bff397fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长取消除“英雄主义”之外的所有以色列奖奖项类别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-cancels-all-israel-prize-awards-categories-except-for-heroism/0000018d-bbfe-dd5e-a59d-fffe21930000</link><description>今年的以色列奖将不会颁发传统的人文、科学和文化类别，而只会颁发一个类别，其中六名获奖者“在 10 月 7 日发生的可怕危机后为国家的复苏做出了贡献”</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 12:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-cancels-all-israel-prize-awards-categories-except-for-h